data.description: Don't miss this gently lived in one-story home in far west San Antonio.  Located off 1604 near Hwy 90 and Potranco Road.  Easy access to downtown, Lackland AFB, Citibank, and the new Microsoft data center.  Spacious kitchen features granite counter tops and large island overlooking family room.  Master bath has separate shower and tub.  Water softener and reverse osmosis water system valued at $5k.  Covered patio on greenbelt with views of neighborhood elementary school.  Possible VA assumable loan.
